<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-1">Accessibility</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Braille translation service<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Disabled parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Disabled WC<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Induction loop<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Text Relay<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="no">Signing service available<span class="hidden"> (no)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Wheelchair access<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Step free access<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContent575f5f88f5ab4c7dab5591232cbcec64">
<div class="profile-pic">
<img alt="Positive about disability" border="0" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_column3Content_column3Content_FacilityGroupsRepeater_ctl00_FacilityGroupModule_PhotoView_DisplayImage" src="/Services/UserControls/UploadHandlers/MediaServerHandler.ashx?id=41182"/>
</div>
</div>
<p>Disabled car parking is avaible in most of our car parking areas. We also have a drop off point outside our main hospital entrance, where wheelchairs can be requested.</p>
<p>You can also view <a href="http://stockporthealth.directenquiries.com/search/who/0/0/0/0/UK/Stockport NHS Foundation Trust/0/0/0/0/0/23892/search.aspx" target="_self">accessibility information for Stepping Hill Hospital here</a>.</p>
</div>
<div class="col two-sm last">
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="col clear facility">
<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-2">Accommodation</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Access to TV<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Internet access<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Public telephone<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="no">Family accommodation<span class="hidden"> (no)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Mobile phones permitted<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="no">Private rooms only<span class="hidden"> (no)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Single sex accommodation only<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContentb4eccf12f6984336a3ec93e0ce259ef4">
<div class="profile-pic">
<img alt="Maternity room" border="0" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_column3Content_column3Content_FacilityGroupsRepeater_ctl01_FacilityGroupModule_PhotoView_DisplayImage" src="/Services/UserControls/UploadHandlers/MediaServerHandler.ashx?id=41187"/>
</div>
</div>
<p>We want your stay with us to be as comfortable as possible.Â Things to bring with you may include: night wear; slippers; dressing gown; toiletries, including soap and shampoo; toothbrush; toothpaste/denture cleaner; newspapers; books, etc. Regretably, a personal laundry service cannot be offered.</p>
<p>For further useful information about coming into Stepping Hill Hospital <a href="https://www.stockport.nhs.uk/page.aspx?id=32" target="_self">click here</a>.</p>
</div>
<div class="col two-sm last">
</div>
</div>
