<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="col clear facility">
<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-3">Bringing children to Stepping Hill Hospital</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Baby changing facility<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Children's play area<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Parent and child parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Parent and baby room<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="no">Pram park<span class="hidden"> (no)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContent01b445b5a73d4b0e9a762ea4656ed6b7">
<div class="profile-pic">
<img alt="Tree House children's unit" border="0" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_column3Content_column3Content_FacilityGroupsRepeater_ctl02_FacilityGroupModule_PhotoView_DisplayImage" src="/Services/UserControls/UploadHandlers/MediaServerHandler.ashx?id=41192"/>
</div>
</div>
<p>There are play areas with toys in most of our outpatient departments. For safety reasons, please ensure that your children are supervised at all times.</p>
<p>We also have free wifi in most of our outpatient and food service areas.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.stockport.nhs.uk/page.aspx?id=50" target="_self">Click here</a> for mor euseful visitor information.</p>
</div>
<div class="col two-sm last">
</div>
</div>
</div>
