</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="col clear facility">
<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-5">Faith services</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Prayer area<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">On-site chapel<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContent704637cc5dbf4405bd0e9639d58242e2">
<div class="profile-pic">
<img alt="Multi-faith chapel" border="0" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_column3Content_column3Content_FacilityGroupsRepeater_ctl04_FacilityGroupModule_PhotoView_DisplayImage" src="/Services/UserControls/UploadHandlers/MediaServerHandler.ashx?id=41188"/>
</div>
</div>
<p>The hospital recognises that you may have spiritual needs. A team of chaplains is employed by the Trust to visit the wards regularly.  Please ask if you wish to see a chaplain.  Representatives of other faith groups are available by request.</p>
<p>The hospital chapel, a multi-faith room, is situated in the Chaplaincy Centre on the main corridor.  The chapel is always open for quiet prayer.</p>
</div>
<div class="col two-sm last">
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="col clear facility">
<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-6">Food and amenities on-site</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Cafe<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Patient library<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Pharmacy<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Shop<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContenta22a8d7e68614c62b5ebb61965881288">
<div class="profile-pic">
<img alt="On-site pharmacy" border="0" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_column3Content_column3Content_FacilityGroupsRepeater_ctl05_FacilityGroupModule_PhotoView_DisplayImage" src="/Services/UserControls/UploadHandlers/MediaServerHandler.ashx?id=41190"/>
</div>
</div>
<p>Stepping Hill Hospital provides a wide range of hot and cold food, drinks and refreshments from our restaurant, cafe and shops throughout the site. Everyone is welcome to use these facilities.</p>
<p>We also have an outpatient pharmacy and free wifi in most outpatinet and food service areas.</p>
<p>Wheelchairs are available at the hospitals main entrance and our volunteers are also located here to assist.</p>
<p>Click <a href="https://www.stockport.nhs.uk/page.aspx?id=50" target="_self">here</a> for more information.<br/>The hospital operates a no-smoking policy across the whole site.</p>
</div>
<div class="col two-sm last">
</div>
