<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-7">Parking</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Car Parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Cycle parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Disabled parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContent590a6e8cf7ad4bfaaa35002b2f7a6a5a">
<div class="profile-pic">
<img alt="Car parking at Stepping Hill Hospital" border="0" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_column3Content_column3Content_FacilityGroupsRepeater_ctl06_FacilityGroupModule_PhotoView_DisplayImage" src="/Services/UserControls/UploadHandlers/MediaServerHandler.ashx?id=41193"/>
</div>
</div>
<p>You can park in the various car parking spaces around the site, however there are a limited number of spaces available. All car parking spaces are pay and display. You must pay for and display a valid car parking ticket when leaving your car.Â </p>
<p>Car parking charges are as follows:</p>
<ul>
<li>Up to 2 hours: Â£3.50</li>
<li>2-4 hours: Â£6.00</li>
<li>More than 4 hours: Â£8.00</li>
</ul>
<p>Disabled car parking spaces are free of charge, however a valid blue badge must be displayed clearly on the vehicle.Â </p>
